<!-- Node: "Half-Life Mappers Mailing List" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Half-Life Mappers Mailing List</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/31" title="View user profile.">mazemaster</a> on Saturday, May 22, 2004 - 02:28</small><br /><br />
Autolycus at the <a href="http://www.valve-erc.com">VERC</a> announced that Valve has established a <a href = "http://list.valvesoftware.com/mailman/listinfo/hlmappers">Half-Life Mappers Mailing List</a>. The original post on the collective can be seen <a href = "http://collective.valve-erc.com/index.php?news=1085090335-84148300">here</a>.<br />
<br />
Eventually this will become the HL2 mapping mailing list.
